There is a cat here. She doesn't seem to mind the rain.
Give her your piece of jerky?
The cat grabs it out of your hand and eats it, making loud noises the entire time.
Once she's finished, she looks up at you.
The cat makes her way to your lap and sits in it.
You are instantly calmed by the sounds of her purrs and the sound of the rain.
She's a good cat. A really good cat.
Her name is Cassie. She was named after the constellation, Cassiopeia.
Even if you're a stranger, she'll approach you and give you affection.
Thank you for giving her your time.
